.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.
Welcome to the Elven Lands. The Elven
Lands are filled with many,many
quests,and fine rewards. These maps
have a unique,interesting plot and
story line. Different guilds and
circles of magic are spread throughout
the continent. Shops are in
abundance, there are countless secrets
to be found. Beware, you must have a
good mind, there are many puzzles and
riddles along the way. Good luck!
